name: gProfiler_pvalue_filter
description: Filters the gProfiler enrichemnt results by a p_value threshold

inputs.value:
import pandas as pd

enrichment_data = {enrichment_data}
pvalue_threshold = '''{pvalue_threshold}'''

# filter by pvalue
pvalue_threshold = float(pvalue_threshold)

df = pd.DataFrame(enrichment_data)

df_f = df.loc[df['p_value'] < pvalue_threshold]

df_f = df_f.to_dict()

# result

result = df_f
